code: @Override public T onRdd(JavaRDDLike rdd, Object... payloads) {     if (payloads.length != payloadsTypes.length) {         String message = format("Received %d payloads, but expected %d.", payloads.length, payloadsTypes.length).         throw new IllegalArgumentException(message).     }     for (int i = 0. i < payloads.length. i++) {         payloads[i] = camelContext.getTypeConverter().convertTo(payloadsTypes[i], payloads[i]).     }     return doOnRdd(rdd, payloads). }
public abstract T doOnRdd(JavaRDDLike rdd, Object... payloads).
